1DD7F3D1.Line13.137EC4: Bring them to me, and we will show the Triune that Oxen craft endures.

3FF43762.Line5.137EC4: It must be repaired, Raekor’s glory returned to its edge.

45544A0F.Line11.137EC4: Silver Quartz will mend the haft. It’s a rare find within the caves to the north.

67708DA0.Line3.137EC4: The haft is destroyed, and the head will fracture before it reaches any bone.

8EECE3DE.Line1.137EC4: Decades with our Warmaster, not a scratch. Days with the Triune...shattered. Disgraceful.

F0FB8AE6.Line9.137EC4: I require a demon’s horn to reforge the head. A fiend hardened by fire, like those found within the eastern crags.

FB3FFC35.MenuLabel: “I retrieved the great axe. It was damaged by the Triune.”
